\f0\fs28 \cf2 in particular, ||x||^2 = sum (alpha square) index from 1 to n}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf190
{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue-Bold;\f1\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue;}
{\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;\red6\green53\blue51;}
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 lemma: 
\f1\b0 \cf2 \{e_n\} an orthonormal set in an inner product space V. if x = sum each vector times its coefficient alpha_i, and y = sum of each vector times another coefficient beta_i, then <x, y> = sum(alpha_i times beta_i).}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf190
{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue-Bold;\f1\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue;}
{\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;\red6\green53\blue51;}
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 corollary: 
\f1\b0 \cf2 an inner product space of dimension n has an orthonormal basis with n elements.}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf190
{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue-Light;\f1\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue;\f2\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue-Bold;
}
{\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;\red6\green53\blue51;}
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural

\f0\fs28 \cf2 def: 
\f1 \cf2 a 
\f2\b \cf2 projection 
\f1\b0 \cf2 on an inner product space V is a linear map P: from V to V such that P^2 = P. in addition we say that P is an 
\f2\b \cf2 orthogonal projection 
\f1\b0 \cf2 if kerP = \{v in V : Pv = 0\} is orthogonal to ranP = PV}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf190
{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue;}
{\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;\red6\green53\blue51;}
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural

\f0\fs28 \cf2 2. for all x in V, ||x||^2 = ||Px||^2 + ||(I-P)x||^2}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf190
{\fonttbl\f0\fnil\fcharset0 HelveticaNeue;}
{\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;\red6\green53\blue51;}
