\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 corollary: 
\f1\b0 \cf2 let E = \{e_n : n in S\} be an orthonormal set in a Hilbert space H. then there is a continuous linear orthogonal projection P_M of H onto M = spanE^bar given by P_M_x = sigma(<x, e_n>e_n)}

